Package teal.sim.simulation

Provides the interface for any TEALsim simulation as well as a base class which may be extended or created via a SimulationFactory.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TSimulation
    The TSimulation provides a interface for the specification and management of all elements related to a specific simulation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SimDrawOrder
    Provides the Comparator used to order a sorted list of rendered objects.
    Simulation3D
    The abstract class Simulation3D implements TSimulation and provides management for a simulation which includes a 3D viewer and simulation engine specified in a derived class.
    Simulation3DBeanInfo  
    SimulationFactory
    Provides the ability to create a TSimulation from an XML input stream and to dump a TSimulation into an XML output stream.
    SimWorld
    The SimWorld provides management for a simulation with a default 3D viewer and and SimEngine.
    tealsim
    Implements a ContentHandler for the creation of TSimulation objects from a URL with mimetype of "simultation/tealsim".

Package teal.sim.simulation Description

Provides the interface for any TEALsim simulation as well as a base class which may be extended or created via a SimulationFactory. This sentence is here to prevent errors being generated in javadoc generation.
